title: League of Legends BRAUM Login Theme on piano

embed.description: Hello :) Here is my upload for November. I really loved to play this song, even though I had to cut it into 2 parts, due to low practice and recording time. League of Legends is after 4 years still my favourite game and maybe I'll play some more songs from it.

body:
Hallo Leute,
ich habe das Titelthema von Braum auf dem Klavier gespielt. Ich hoffe, dass es euch gefällt :)

replies.body:
Geklickt habe ich wegen der Poros, geblieben bin ich wegen der Musik. :D

{{summoner:31}}
